{"tid":2412423,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿朗冤啊！明顯12碼被無視！雲格：是12碼","createTime":"2021-02-18T04:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T09:50:55.000Z","uid":173952,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5a74d6a2bae152ad50613464d4a212953ec93d","tid":2412423,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/446/w277h169/20210218/ed8e-kkciesr1373254.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F446%2Fw277h169%2F20210218%2Fed8e-kkciesr1373254.gif&h=0b757caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC.朗拿度12碼被漏判了<br />\n<br />\n  歐聯16強首回合，祖雲達斯作客1-2輸給波圖，在這場比賽快結束時，出現了極具爭議的一幕。<br />\n<br />\n  當時C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）禁區內停球，和對手身體接觸後倒地，VAR並沒有對這次倒地進行審查，這引起了爭議。<br />\n<br />\n  作客《拜因體育》的嘉賓雲格（Arsene Wenger）和古烈治（Ruud Gullit）都認為，這應該是一粒12碼，VAR明顯犯錯誤了"},{"pid":"bf276b70c7465955d4a7e5a32f982c1ef6c02970","tid":2412423,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:32:56.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺是對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7097ab1a10c6604b132cd3692658aad89d776164","tid":2412423,"uid":1977,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"返曼聯囉"},{"pid":"cd40a8fc4bc391d88a36832a07bdfee4e7e04ae5","tid":2412423,"uid":132322,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:58:21.000Z","msg":"C朗先生沒有輸，到最後一刻仍然想插水博十二碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f999bcceec93bdb7e633d855af9cf986200ce8","tid":2412423,"uid":385717,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"用巴塞尋晚果場個標準<br />\n呢球都要比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f68a1f9197c1fe2f6bf9f0755893d99dec43e9","tid":2412423,"uid":35176,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"qu